<div class="swapable-text" id="overview-text" style="display:block;">
    <a href="/Sales/privateHostedCloudList/VMHOST/1"><img src="http://static.softlayer.com/images/blackTheme/buttons/build-now-private-cloud.png" alt="Place an Order" class="rightSideButton"/></a>
    <a href="#"><img id="private-cloud-chat-button" class="rightSideButton" src="http://static.softlayer.com/images/blackTheme/buttons/chat-live-now-232x36.png" alt="Chat with our hosting experts"/></a>
    <a href="http://www.citrix.com/English/ps2/products/product.asp?contentID=2314749&ntref=prod_cat"><img src="http://static.softlayer.com/images/blackTheme/logos/citrix-cloudplatform-logo.png" alt="Citrix CloudPlatform powered by Apache CloudStack" class="rightSideButton moreMarginTop"  /></a>

    <h2 class="noTopMargin">Deploy and scale your own private cloud at the push of a button. Introducing full cloud solutions with
        automated provisioning and configuration.</h2>

    <p>We’ve automated everything, so your Private Cloud can be ready in just a couple hours. Instead of starting at
        square one, you start with a whole cloud ready for whatever you want to do with it, with total access and
        control over every aspect.</p>

    <p class="noMarginBottom">Our system automatically:</p>
    <ul class="standardList moreMarginBottom noTopMargin">
        <li><span>provisions your Management Server and installs its management system.</span></li>
        <li><span>provisions your Host Servers and installs each host’s hypervisor.</span></li>
        <li><span>registers your Host Servers with the Management Server.</span></li>
        <li><span>completes additional network and resource management tasks.</span></li>
    </ul>

    <p>SoftLayer Private Clouds are now available with Citrix CloudPlatform, powered by Apache CloudStack, as the cloud
        management solution. CloudPlatform’s flexibility and ease of use provide the control, efficiency, and
        scalability that innovative private cloud solutions require.</p>

    <p>And, as with all SoftLayer services, your Private Cloud can function as a stand-alone environment, or be fully
        integrated with your other SoftLayer solutions and services, including dedicated and cloud servers,
        database clusters, content delivery network, and more.</p>

    <p>If you’ve been waiting for a cloud of your own, your wait is over. We’ve put together the solution that puts your
        private cloud in the sky today.</p>

    <p><a href="/Sales/privateHostedCloudList/VMHOST/1" class="slRed plainLink">Order now</a>, or <a href="#" id="private-cloud-chat-link1" class="slRed plainLink">click to chat</a> for more information.</p>

    <div id="related_topics" class="related_topics_style_box">
        <h3>Key Advantages</h3>

        <div class="related_topic_details">
            <h4>Automated Deployment, On-Demand Scalability</h4>
            <p>Deploy the cloud you want, when you need it, and add physical nodes and virtual servers at any time.</p>

            <h4>Full Management Access and Control</h4>
            <p>Keep total control over your private cloud via our web portal, full-featured API, and CloudStack management
                tools.</p>

            <h4>Seamless Global Deployment</h4>
            <p>Our global data center and private network footprint let you deploy Private Cloud zones in any SoftLayer data
                center, and control them from a single management server anywhere else.</p>

            <h4>SoftLayer Object Storage Integration</h4>
            <p>Share virtual machine images, files, and other data resources across your private cloud with our advanced,
                searchable Object Storage solution.</p>

            <h4>RightScale Integration</h4>
            <p>Deploy and manage your private cloud using RightScale myCloud on the RightScale Cloud Management Platform to
                leverage RightScale ServerTemplates, RightScripts, and more.</p>

        </div>
    </div>


    <h2 class="extraHeading2 clear-element">Sample Use Cases</h2>

    <h4 class="slRed">Seasonal E-Commerce Site</h4>

    <p>Meet seasonal demand with ease. SoftLayer Private Clouds lets you add new host servers to your environment in
        only a few hours, and spin up VMs in real time. Be prepared for and quickly respond to traffic spikes during
        peak season, and easily scale back during slower periods.</p>

    <h4 class="slRed">Rich Media Rendering Companies</h4>

    <p>Private Clouds provides an easier, more efficient solution to cumbersome and compute-intensive infrastructure by
        providing the scalability and elasticity you need to complete rendering processes while balancing workload
        across entire infrastructure.</p>

    <h4 class="slRed">Scalable Web Apps</h4>

    <p>We designed Private Clouds to simplify web app development and deployment by giving you the ability to quickly
        spin up a turnkey cloud, burst instantly to meet demand, scale incrementally, and more. All built on the
        industry’s most advanced, durable, and robust cloud platform.</p>

<div class="back-next-inpage-navigation">                <div class="back-next-inpage-navigation-right-arrow" onclick="sectionSwapAdv('pricing',true);"></div>
                <div class="back-next-inpage-navigation-right-text" onclick="sectionSwapAdv('pricing',true);">Pricing</div></div></div>

<div class="swapable-text" id="pricing-text">
<h2>Pricing</h2>

<p>With automated provisioning and on demand scalability, SoftLayer Private Clouds saves you the time and cost of
    deploying and configuring your own private cloud solution, and streamlines management through your private cloud’s
    life cycle.</p>

<p>Every SoftLayer Private Cloud consists of a standard management server—chosen and configured to meet the exact needs
    of the cloud management system—SoftLayer Object Storage, and your choice of a range of host servers. Select as many
    host servers as you require, and customize their resources, including RAM and storage, to your desired
    specifications.</p>

<p>SoftLayer Private Clouds are provisioned in two to four hours and offered with month-to-month contracts.</p>

<p><a href="/Sales/privateHostedCloudList/VMHOST/1" class="slRed plainLink">Order today</a>, or <a href="#" id="private-cloud-chat-link2" class="slRed plainLink">click to chat</a> for more information.</p>

